my life for a while,

479
00:23:23,756 --> 00:23:25,891
and I just--

480
00:23:25,958 --> 00:23:27,592
I want to protect
you from this stuff.

481
00:23:27,660 --> 00:23:29,928
We've got something
really special, Ryan.

482
00:23:29,996 --> 00:23:31,997
I know you feel it, too.

483
00:23:32,065 --> 00:23:34,966
Don't be so quick
to throw us away.

484
00:23:36,836 --> 00:23:39,337
Ryan, we got a hit
on our grieving father.

485
00:23:39,405 --> 00:23:40,806
Andrew Jacobs.

486
00:23:40,873 --> 00:23:42,007
His driver's license
was issued 10 months ago.

487
00:23:42,075 --> 00:23:43,275
