00:26:53,698 --> 00:26:54,832
It's a tableau

503
00:26:54,899 --> 00:26:57,000
of Max shooting Luke.

504
00:27:01,906 --> 00:27:03,707
You're right.

505
00:27:03,775 --> 00:27:05,742
I was standing in the doorway.

506
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,481
Mike, you were
on the ground there.

507
00:27:13,785 --> 00:27:15,953
