00:28:33,598 --> 00:28:34,832
Ok, ok, everybody.
Listen up.

536
00:28:34,899 --> 00:28:36,467
Our boy Mark is punishing us

537
00:28:36,534 --> 00:28:37,814
for killing
his family last year.

